      "cvss_notes": "CVSS v3.1 AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:N = 9.1 (Critical). Network-reachable via any protocol using AES with attacker-influenced plaintext/IV (TLS, IPsec, GCM/CTR). Full key disclosure -> confidentiality + integrity compromise of entire crypto trust boundary."
